# ----- Commit Rules -----
# 1. Header (first line) MUST NOT exceed 50 characters.
# 2. Format: <type>(Phase <N>): <title>
#    Example: feat(Phase 8): add property access
# 3. Allowed <type>: feat, fix, ci, docs, style, refactor, test, chore
# ------------------------

# Describe "Why" and "Impact"
# - List of changes...
# - Reference Issue or Task ID (if any)
